 it's now been almost two months since the worst
 terror attack on a u.s. navy ship, the destroyer "cole,"
 and tonight, sources tell nbc news that an american muslim
 militant, a prime suspect in planning the attack, is now
 in custody in jordan. his name is jayed hijazi,
 and nbc news has learned he's got direct high-level ties
 to the terrorist osama bin laden.
 he's reportedly told u.s. investigators of additional
 plans, to attack u.s. military aircraft in the persian gulf
 and middle east. 
